data.author: Guillaume Beuzeboc
data.message:
fix(CI): remove MacOS CI (#48)

Because of
https://github.com/actions/runner-images/issues/6507#issuecomment-1301636292
Installing and running Python packages is no longer straightforward
Even with a temporary fix, rclpy was no longer building on MacOS
